---
description: Persist useful project context and decisions into workspace context files during normal work.
alwaysApply: true
---

- Load existing project context files before starting work when relevant.
- Persist durable context (research, decisions, reusable templates, constraints) to workspace files.
- Prefer append-with-date updates over overwriting accumulated context.
- Keep saved context scannable with clear file names and concise structure.
- Save non-trivial learnings before ending a task so future sessions can reuse them.
- Avoid saving trivial or easily re-derived information.
